<item>
            <title>[BEAM-1556] Spark executors need to register IO factories</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/BEAM-1556</link>
                <project id="12319527" key="BEAM">Beam</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Spark executors need to call IOChannelUtils.registerIOFactories(options) in order to support GCS file and make the default WordCount example work.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Context in this thread: &lt;a href=&quot;https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/469a139c9eb07e64e514cdea42ab8000678ab743794a090c365205d7@%3Cuser.beam.apache.org%3E&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://lists.apache.org/thread.html/469a139c9eb07e64e514cdea42ab8000678ab743794a090c365205d7@%3Cuser.beam.apache.org%3E&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13046347">BEAM-1556</key>
            <summary>Spark executors need to register IO factories</summary>
